===============================================================================
        1     -     Installation
===============================================================================

Linux/Ubuntu installation
    
    Ubuntu Libaries required:
    -lGL
    -lGLU 
    -lSDL2 
    -lGLEW
    
    Install
    GL:     sudo apt-get install libgl1-mesa-dev
    GLU:    sudo apt-get install libglu1-mesa-dev 
    SDL2:    sudo apt-get install libsdl2-dev
    GLEW:    sudo apt-get install libglew-dev
    
    Build Mango using makefile
        make

Mac installation
    
    Mac Frameworks required:
    OpenGL
    SDL2
    GLEW

    SDL2 download framework from website:
    Copy framework file to Libary/Frameworks

    GLEW download glew from website:
    Build and install with make file
    make
    make install

    Build Mango using makefile
        make mac

Windows installation

    Make sure dll are all in correct folder


