===============================================================================
        3     -     Command line arguments
===============================================================================

Command line arguments
    -f <flie_path>
    -start <start_num>
    -num <num>
    -arrow
    -cube
    -sphere
    -circle
    -point
    -obj <waveobj_file_path>


===============================================================================
        4     -     Keyboard controls
===============================================================================

Arrow Left               - Back one time step
Arrow Right              - Forward one time step

Number keys 1-9          - Toggle show material 1-9

Space bar                - Toggle camera or object movement

w/s                      - Move Object/Camera Forward/Backward
a/d                      - Move Object/Camera Left/Right
q/e                      - Move Object/Camera Up/Down

i/o                      - Rotate Roll
j/k                      - Rotate Pitch
n/m                      - Rotate Yaw

t                        - Show framerate

escape                   - Close Program